         <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="Section_H">
            
            
            <xs:annotation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed Heat Pump System - Split System Condensing Unit or Package Unit Equipment Information</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">This Section is applicable only if at least one  system in section D has D04_ResidentialHeatingSystemType Or  
D05_ResidentialCoolingSystemType ==  CentralLargePackagedHP, CentralPackagedHP, CentralSplitHP,  DuctlessSplitHP (display term Ductless mini-split HP), DuctedMiniSplitHP, 
AirToWaterHeatPump, GroundSourceHeatPump, DuctedMultiSplitHP, DuctlessMultiSplitHP, DuctedDuctlessMultiSplitHP, DuctlessVRF_HP, SmallDuctHighVelocityHP, HydronicHP, 
HydronicHP_ForcedAir, RoomHP,  VCHP_IndoorUnitDucted, VCHP_IndoorUnitDuctless, VCHP_IndoorUnitDuctedAndDuctless Or HeatPumpDHWCombo. Require one row of data in this table for each of the SC Systems listed in Section B that is  in this list.</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="MinOccurs">If this section doesn't apply, display only the section FieldText and the statement 'This section does not apply to this project.'</xs:documentation>
               
            
